In re Resignation of Muldrow.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Muldrow (1992), 63 Ohio St.3d 1210.]

(No. 92-416 Submitted March 17, 1992 Decided April 1, 1992.)

The resignation of Norris Muldrow as an attorney, Registration No. 0033138, is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
